  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Especially with the-- with my Polish friends, I was skating with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What's-- I mentioned before, I would-- I hate to repeat myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's the only thing where the-- I associated-- the-- they liked me, because they thought-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They thought-- I act like they-- I'm-- the-- Polish people was different to say, the Jewish people-- different dress, different-- with always some of them with accent-- not all of them-- like myself.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] This is the reason they associate with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- and-- and I enjoyed them, because they been-- good-- very good athletes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I consider myself a good athlete in-- in the-- even now, I think-- I believe longevity if I'm-- already now 80-- 82 years.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because I've been, all my life a good athlete-- a good soccer player, a good bicycle, a good-- especially ice skating.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I loved ice skating until today.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I even think someday I feel another-- because now I'm after serious surgery, I will feel better.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I go back skating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I got fine skates.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I paid a few hundred dollar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I couldn't afford it as something-- a kid in Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I couldn't afford it, something like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not the reason, because I tried to keep myself at a distance from them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have give them a chance to see me different, because I had been a good athlete, and I'd been-- I-- we associated with the-- the Polish girls.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to go on-- even I belonged to entire-- when I come home from there, I-- I-- I like I-- I-- I got two personalities in myself-- one personality way to Zionism, to this movement.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I feel myself, like, very close.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
